content: i created this little guy for the kitty lovin hookers group charity cal i called this chirp at the birdie because thats what i call what my cats do when they see birds outside they make this chattering meh-eh-eh-eh-eh sound and we ve always said they were chirping at the birds i learned here that this is a hunter instinct and that it is their way of laying claim to that prize like stay away from that one its mine im gonna get it
